title: Ebro In The Morning - The Kanye Saga Continues + The Day After Valentines
itunes:author: Ebro In The Morning on HOT 97
itunes:summary:
Ebro, Rosenberg and Laura Stylez star in HOT97's flagship program Ebro in the Morning - this episode aired on 2/15/2022.

Ebro, Rosenberg, Laura Stylez, and the crew are in the studio talking about the Kanye West saga (16) and the day after Valentine's Day (53). Get excited for the gurus to help solve your problems. All that and more on Ebro In The Morning!
